{
  "video_id": "YKACzIrog24",
  "title": "How to get better at the things you care about | Eduardo Brice√±o",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 16596.0,
      "text": "Most of us go through life trying to do our best at whatever we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16620.0,
      "end_time": 19196.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s our job, family, school"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19220.0,
      "end_time": 20419.0,
      "text": "or anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21600.0,
      "end_time": 22860.0,
      "text": "I feel that way. I try my best."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23740.0,
      "end_time": 26636.0,
      "text": "But some time ago, I came to a realization"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26660.0,
      "end_time": 30436.0,
      "text": "that I wasn&#39;t getting much better at the things I cared most about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30460.0,
      "end_time": 33636.0,
      "text": "whether it was being a husband or a friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33660.0,
      "end_time": 35876.0,
      "text": "or a professional or teammate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35900.0,
      "end_time": 37916.0,
      "text": "and I wasn&#39;t improving much at those things"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37940.0,
      "end_time": 40476.0,
      "text": "even though I was spending a lot of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 41700.0,
      "text": "working hard at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43200.0,
      "end_time": 46396.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve since realized from conversations I&#39;ve had and from research"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46420.0,
      "end_time": 49760.0,
      "text": "that this stagnation, despite hard work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49100.0,
      "end_time": 50836.0,
      "text": "turns out to be pretty common."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50860.0,
      "end_time": 53716.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to share with you some insights into why that is"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53740.0,
      "end_time": 55264.0,
      "text": "and what we can all do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55980.0,
      "end_time": 58476.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;ve learned is that the most effective people"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58500.0,
      "end_time": 60476.0,
      "text": "and teams in any domain"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60500.0,
      "end_time": 62140.0,
      "text": "do something we can all emulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62820.0,
      "end_time": 66876.0,
      "text": "They go through life deliberately alternating between two zones:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66900.0,
      "end_time": 68980.0,
      "text": "the learning zone and the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69980.0,
      "end_time": 72636.0,
      "text": "The learning zone is when our goal is to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72660.0,
      "end_time": 75756.0,
      "text": "Then we do activities designed for improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75780.0,
      "end_time": 78236.0,
      "text": "concentrating on what we haven&#39;t mastered yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80716.0,
      "text": "which means we have to expect to make mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80740.0,
      "end_time": 82539.0,
      "text": "knowing that we will learn from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82980.0,
      "end_time": 86716.0,
      "text": "That is very different from what we do when we&#39;re in our performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86740.0,
      "end_time": 91360.0,
      "text": "which is when our goal is to do something as best as we can, to execute."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91600.0,
      "end_time": 93676.0,
      "text": "Then we concentrate on what we have already mastered"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93700.0,
      "end_time": 95460.0,
      "text": "and we try to minimize mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96660.0,
      "end_time": 99760.0,
      "text": "Both of these zones should be part of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99100.0,
      "end_time": 102356.0,
      "text": "but being clear about when we want to be in each of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102380.0,
      "end_time": 104676.0,
      "text": "with what goal, focus and expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104700.0,
      "end_time": 107516.0,
      "text": "helps us better perform and better improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107540.0,
      "end_time": 110476.0,
      "text": "The performance zone maximizes our immediate performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110500.0,
      "end_time": 112596.0,
      "text": "while the learning zone maximizes our growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112620.0,
      "end_time": 113906.0,
      "text": "and our future performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115140.0,
      "end_time": 117196.0,
      "text": "The reason many of us don&#39;t improve much"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117220.0,
      "end_time": 118956.0,
      "text": "despite our hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118980.0,
      "end_time": 122980.0,
      "text": "is that we tend to spend almost all of our time in the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123700.0,
      "end_time": 125760.0,
      "text": "This hinders our growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125100.0,
      "end_time": 128180.0,
      "text": "and ironically, over the long term, also our performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129860.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131820.0,
      "text": "So what does the learning zone look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132580.0,
      "end_time": 134596.0,
      "text": "Take Demosthenes, a political leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134620.0,
      "end_time": 137460.0,
      "text": "and the greatest orator and lawyer in ancient Greece."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138600.0,
      "end_time": 141715.0,
      "text": "To become great, he didn&#39;t spend all his time"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141739.0,
      "end_time": 144156.0,
      "text": "just being an orator or a lawyer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 144180.0,
      "end_time": 146356.0,
      "text": "which would be his performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146380.0,
      "end_time": 149000.0,
      "text": "But instead, he did activities designed for improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149420.0,
      "end_time": 150796.0,
      "text": "Of course, he studied a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150820.0,
      "end_time": 153636.0,
      "text": "He studied law and philosophy with guidance from mentors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153660.0,
      "end_time": 158196.0,
      "text": "but he also realized that being a lawyer involved persuading other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158220.0,
      "end_time": 160596.0,
      "text": "so he also studied great speeches"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160620.0,
      "end_time": 161820.0,
      "text": "and acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162460.0,
      "end_time": 166756.0,
      "text": "To get rid of an odd habit he had of involuntarily lifting his shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166780.0,
      "end_time": 169196.0,
      "text": "he practiced his speeches in front of a mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169220.0,
      "end_time": 172196.0,
      "text": "and he suspended a sword from the ceiling"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172220.0,
      "end_time": 173956.0,
      "text": "so that if he raised his shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173980.0,
      "end_time": 175196.0,
      "text": "it would hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 175220.0,
      "end_time": 176836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176860.0,
      "end_time": 178996.0,
      "text": "To speak more clearly despite a lisp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179200.0,
      "end_time": 181860.0,
      "text": "he went through his speeches with stones in his mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 182660.0,
      "end_time": 184360.0,
      "text": "He built an underground room"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 184600.0,
      "end_time": 186196.0,
      "text": "where he could practice without interruptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 186220.0,
      "end_time": 187636.0,
      "text": "and not disturb other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 187660.0,
      "end_time": 189796.0,
      "text": "And since courts at the time were very noisy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189820.0,
      "end_time": 191676.0,
      "text": "he also practiced by the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191700.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "projecting his voice above the roar of the waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 195220.0,
      "end_time": 196916.0,
      "text": "His activities in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 196940.0,
      "end_time": 199436.0,
      "text": "were very different from his activities in court,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 199460.0,
      "end_time": 200740.0,
      "text": "his performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201580.0,
      "end_time": 202796.0,
      "text": "In the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 202820.0,
      "end_time": 205596.0,
      "text": "he did what Dr. Anders Ericsson calls deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205620.0,
      "end_time": 209156.0,
      "text": "This involves breaking down abilities into component skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209180.0,
      "end_time": 212760.0,
      "text": "being clear about what subskill we&#39;re working to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212100.0,
      "end_time": 214760.0,
      "text": "like keeping our shoulders down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214100.0,
      "end_time": 216956.0,
      "text": "giving full concentration to a high level of challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216980.0,
      "end_time": 218396.0,
      "text": "outside our comfort zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 218420.0,
      "end_time": 220756.0,
      "text": "just beyond what we can currently do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 220780.0,
      "end_time": 223996.0,
      "text": "using frequent feedback with repetition and adjustments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 224200.0,
      "end_time": 226996.0,
      "text": "and ideally engaging the guidance of a skilled coach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 227200.0,
      "end_time": 229760.0,
      "text": "because activities designed for improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 229100.0,
      "end_time": 230356.0,
      "text": "are domain-specific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 230380.0,
      "end_time": 233275.0,
      "text": "and great teachers and coaches know what those activities are"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233300.0,
      "end_time": 235180.0,
      "text": "and can also give us expert feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 235780.0,
      "end_time": 238476.0,
      "text": "It is this type of practice in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238500.0,
      "end_time": 240396.0,
      "text": "which leads to substantial improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 240420.0,
      "end_time": 242780.0,
      "text": "not just time on task performing."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 243780.0,
      "end_time": 246956.0,
      "text": "For example, research shows that after the first couple of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 246980.0,
      "end_time": 248236.0,
      "text": "working in a profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250596.0,
      "text": "performance usually plateaus."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 250620.0,
      "end_time": 253676.0,
      "text": "This has been shown to be true in teaching, general medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253700.0,
      "end_time": 255396.0,
      "text": "nursing and other fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255420.0,
      "end_time": 259156.0,
      "text": "and it happens because once we think we have become good enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 259180.0,
      "end_time": 260396.0,
      "text": "adequate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 260420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262676.0,
      "text": "then we stop spending time in the learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 262700.0,
      "end_time": 264876.0,
      "text": "We focus all our time on just doing our job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 264900.0,
      "end_time": 266116.0,
      "text": "performing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 266140.0,
      "end_time": 268460.0,
      "text": "which turns out not to be a great way to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 268980.0,
      "end_time": 271916.0,
      "text": "But the people who continue to spend time in the learning zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 271940.0,
      "end_time": 274760.0,
      "text": "do continue to always improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 274100.0,
      "end_time": 276516.0,
      "text": "The best salespeople at least once a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 276540.0,
      "end_time": 279156.0,
      "text": "do activities with the goal of improvement."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 279180.0,
      "end_time": 280956.0,
      "text": "They read to extend their knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 280980.0,
      "end_time": 283396.0,
      "text": "consult with colleagues or domain experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 283420.0,
      "end_time": 286420.0,
      "text": "try out new strategies, solicit feedback and reflect."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287180.0,
      "end_time": 288796.0,
      "text": "The best chess players"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 288820.0,
      "end_time": 292356.0,
      "text": "spend a lot of time not playing games of chess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 292380.0,
      "end_time": 294316.0,
      "text": "which would be their performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 294340.0,
      "end_time": 297820.0,
      "text": "but trying to predict the moves grand masters made and analyzing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 298740.0,
      "end_time": 302836.0,
      "text": "Each of us has probably spent many, many, many hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 302860.0,
      "end_time": 304396.0,
      "text": "typing on a computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 304420.0,
      "end_time": 305996.0,
      "text": "without getting faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 306200.0,
      "end_time": 309436.0,
      "text": "but if we spent 10 to 20 minutes each day"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 309460.0,
      "end_time": 312635.0,
      "text": "fully concentrating on typing 10 to 20 percent faster"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 312660.0,
      "end_time": 314236.0,
      "text": "than our current reliable speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 315515.0,
      "text": "we would get faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315540.0,
      "end_time": 318556.0,
      "text": "especially if we also identified what mistakes we&#39;re making"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318580.0,
      "end_time": 320539.0,
      "text": "and practiced typing those words."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 321220.0,
      "end_time": 322620.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324100.0,
      "end_time": 325836.0,
      "text": "In what other parts of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325860.0,
      "end_time": 327556.0,
      "text": "perhaps that we care more about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327580.0,
      "end_time": 330116.0,
      "text": "are we working hard but not improving much"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 330140.0,
      "end_time": 332460.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re always in the performance zone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334380.0,
      "end_time": 337356.0,
      "text": "Now, this is not to say that the performance zone has no value."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 337380.0,
      "end_time": 338596.0,
      "text": "It very much does."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338620.0,
      "end_time": 341276.0,
      "text": "When I needed a knee surgery, I didn&#39;t tell the surgeon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 341300.0,
      "end_time": 343956.0,
      "text": "\"Poke around in there and focus on what you don&#39;t know.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343980.0,
      "end_time": 344996.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 346620.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;ll learn from your mistakes!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 347500.0,
      "end_time": 350756.0,
      "text": "I looked for a surgeon who I felt would do a good job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 350780.0,
      "end_time": 352419.0,
      "text": "and I wanted her to do a good job."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 352980.0,
      "end_time": 354396.0,
      "text": "Being in the performance zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 354420.0,
      "end_time": 357600.0,
      "text": "allows us to get things done as best as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 357620.0,
      "end_time": 358996.0,
      "text": "It can also be motivating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 359200.0,
      "end_time": 362596.0,
      "text": "and it provides us with information to identify what to focus on next"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 362620.0,
      "end_time": 364916.0,
      "text": "when we go back to the learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 364940.0,
      "end_time": 366636.0,
      "text": "So the way to high performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 366660.0,
      "end_time": 370356.0,
      "text": "is to alternate between the learning zone and the performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 370380.0,
      "end_time": 372916.0,
      "text": "purposefully building our skills in the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 372940.0,
      "end_time": 375340.0,
      "text": "then applying those skills in the performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 376380.0,
      "end_time": 378396.0,
      "text": "When Beyonc√© is on tour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 378420.0,
      "end_time": 381596.0,
      "text": "during the concert, she&#39;s in her performance zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 381620.0,
      "end_time": 384116.0,
      "text": "but every night when she gets back to the hotel room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 384140.0,
      "end_time": 386356.0,
      "text": "she goes right back into her learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 386380.0,
      "end_time": 389156.0,
      "text": "She watches a video of the show that just ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 389180.0,
      "end_time": 391316.0,
      "text": "She identifies opportunities for improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 391340.0,
      "end_time": 393955.0,
      "text": "for herself, her dancers and her camera staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 393980.0,
      "end_time": 395236.0,
      "text": "And the next morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 395260.0,
      "end_time": 398316.0,
      "text": "everyone receives pages of notes with what to adjust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398340.0,
      "end_time": 402316.0,
      "text": "which they then work on during the day before the next performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402340.0,
      "end_time": 403556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a spiral"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 403580.0,
      "end_time": 405156.0,
      "text": "to ever-increasing capabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 405180.0,
      "end_time": 408796.0,
      "text": "but we need to know when we seek to learn, and when we seek to perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 408820.0,
      "end_time": 410876.0,
      "text": "and while we want to spend time doing both,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 410900.0,
      "end_time": 412996.0,
      "text": "the more time we spend in the learning zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 413200.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "the more we&#39;ll improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 415180.0,
      "end_time": 417580.0,
      "text": "So how can we spend more time in the learning zone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 418860.0,
      "end_time": 422360.0,
      "text": "First, we must believe and understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 422600.0,
      "end_time": 423396.0,
      "text": "that we can improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 423420.0,
      "end_time": 424940.0,
      "text": "what we call a growth mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 425660.0,
      "end_time": 428916.0,
      "text": "Second, we must want to improve at that particular skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 428940.0,
      "end_time": 430876.0,
      "text": "There has to be a purpose we care about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 430900.0,
      "end_time": 432500.0,
      "text": "because it takes time and effort."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 433180.0,
      "end_time": 436196.0,
      "text": "Third, we must have an idea about how to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 436220.0,
      "end_time": 437916.0,
      "text": "what we can do to improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 437940.0,
      "end_time": 440516.0,
      "text": "not how I used to practice the guitar as a teenager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 440540.0,
      "end_time": 442636.0,
      "text": "performing songs over and over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 442660.0,
      "end_time": 444140.0,
      "text": "but doing deliberate practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 444780.0,
      "end_time": 448380.0,
      "text": "And fourth, we must be in a low-stakes situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 448980.0,
      "end_time": 451196.0,
      "text": "because if mistakes are to be expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 451220.0,
      "end_time": 454236.0,
      "text": "then the consequence of making them must not be catastrophic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 455500.0,
      "text": "or even very significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 456600.0,
      "end_time": 459756.0,
      "text": "A tightrope walker doesn&#39;t practice new tricks without a net underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 459780.0,
      "end_time": 462395.0,
      "text": "and an athlete wouldn&#39;t set out to first try a new move"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 462420.0,
      "end_time": 463754.0,
      "text": "during a championship match."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 464940.0,
      "end_time": 466596.0,
      "text": "One reason that in our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 466620.0,
      "end_time": 469760.0,
      "text": "we spend so much time in the performance zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 469100.0,
      "end_time": 473180.0,
      "text": "is that our environments often are, unnecessarily, high stakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 474200.0,
      "end_time": 476236.0,
      "text": "We create social risks for one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479116.0,
      "text": "even in schools which are supposed to be all about learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 479140.0,
      "end_time": 481276.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m not talking about standardized tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 481300.0,
      "end_time": 483516.0,
      "text": "I mean that every minute of every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 483540.0,
      "end_time": 486236.0,
      "text": "many students in elementary schools through colleges"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 489676.0,
      "text": "feel that if they make a mistake, others will think less of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 489700.0,
      "end_time": 491635.0,
      "text": "No wonder they&#39;re always stressed out"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 491660.0,
      "end_time": 493900.0,
      "text": "and not taking the risks necessary for learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 494580.0,
      "end_time": 496835.0,
      "text": "But they learn that mistakes are undesirable"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 496860.0,
      "end_time": 498116.0,
      "text": "inadvertently"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 498140.0,
      "end_time": 501635.0,
      "text": "when teachers or parents are eager to hear just correct answers"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 501660.0,
      "end_time": 504316.0,
      "text": "and reject mistakes rather than welcome and examine them"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 504340.0,
      "end_time": 505595.0,
      "text": "to learn from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 505620.0,
      "end_time": 507356.0,
      "text": "or when we look for narrow responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 507380.0,
      "end_time": 509596.0,
      "text": "rather than encourage more exploratory thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 509620.0,
      "end_time": 510956.0,
      "text": "that we can all learn from."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 510980.0,
      "end_time": 514760.0,
      "text": "When all homework or student work has a number or a letter on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 514100.0,
      "end_time": 515836.0,
      "text": "and counts towards a final grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 515860.0,
      "end_time": 519436.0,
      "text": "rather than being used for practice, mistakes, feedback and revision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 519460.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522660.00000000006,
      "text": "we send the message that school is a performance zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 524590.0,
      "end_time": 526116.0,
      "text": "The same is true in our workplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 526140.0,
      "end_time": 530156.0,
      "text": "In the companies I consult with, I often see flawless execution cultures"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 530180.0,
      "end_time": 532756.0,
      "text": "which leaders foster to encourage great work."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 532780.0,
      "end_time": 535315.0,
      "text": "But that leads employees to stay within what they know"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 535340.0,
      "end_time": 536596.0,
      "text": "and not try new things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 536620.0,
      "end_time": 538956.0,
      "text": "so companies struggle to innovate and improve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 538980.0,
      "end_time": 540180.0,
      "text": "and they fall behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 541780.0,
      "end_time": 544760.0,
      "text": "We can create more spaces for growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 544100.0,
      "end_time": 546156.0,
      "text": "by starting conversations with one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 546180.0,
      "end_time": 548459.0,
      "text": "about when we want to be in each zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 549600.0,
      "end_time": 551756.0,
      "text": "What do we want to get better at and how?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 551780.0,
      "end_time": 554780.0,
      "text": "And when do we want to execute and minimize mistakes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 555500.0,
      "end_time": 558516.0,
      "text": "That way, we gain clarity about what success is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 558540.0,
      "end_time": 560620.0,
      "text": "when, and how to best support one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 561820.0,
      "end_time": 564916.0,
      "text": "But what if we find ourselves in a chronic high-stakes setting"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 564940.0,
      "end_time": 567660.0,
      "text": "and we feel we can&#39;t start those conversations yet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 568540.0,
      "end_time": 571636.0,
      "text": "Then here are three things that we can still do as individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 571660.0,
      "end_time": 575939.0,
      "text": "First, we can create low-stakes islands in an otherwise high-stakes sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 576460.0,
      "end_time": 579196.0,
      "text": "These are spaces where mistakes have little consequence."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 579220.0,
      "end_time": 582676.0,
      "text": "For example, we might find a mentor or a trusted colleague"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 582700.0,
      "end_time": 585876.0,
      "text": "with whom we can exchange ideas or have vulnerable conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 585900.0,
      "end_time": 587276.0,
      "text": "or even role-play."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 587300.0,
      "end_time": 590915.0,
      "text": "Or we can ask for feedback-oriented meetings as projects progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 590940.0,
      "end_time": 595760.0,
      "text": "Or we can set aside time to read or watch videos or take online courses."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 595100.0,
      "end_time": 596500.0,
      "text": "Those are just some examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 597180.0,
      "end_time": 601356.0,
      "text": "Second, we can execute and perform as we&#39;re expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 601380.0,
      "end_time": 603956.0,
      "text": "but then reflect on what we could do better next time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 603980.0,
      "end_time": 605236.0,
      "text": "like Beyonc√© does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 607396.0,
      "text": "and we can observe and emulate experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 607420.0,
      "end_time": 610939.0,
      "text": "The observation, reflection and adjustment is a learning zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 611700.0,
      "end_time": 613900.0,
      "text": "And finally, we can lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 614580.0,
      "end_time": 618156.0,
      "text": "and lower the stakes for others by sharing what we want to get better at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 618180.0,
      "end_time": 620675.0,
      "text": "by asking questions about what we don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 620700.0,
      "end_time": 623196.0,
      "text": "by soliciting feedback and by sharing our mistakes"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 623220.0,
      "end_time": 624836.0,
      "text": "and what we&#39;ve learned from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 624860.0,
      "end_time": 626940.0,
      "text": "so that others can feel safe to do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 627580.0,
      "end_time": 631100.0,
      "text": "Real confidence is about modeling ongoing learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 632700.0,
      "end_time": 637156.0,
      "text": "What if, instead of spending our lives doing, doing, doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 637180.0,
      "end_time": 639276.0,
      "text": "performing, performing, performing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 639300.0,
      "end_time": 641579.0,
      "text": "we spent more time exploring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 642460.0,
      "end_time": 643876.0,
      "text": "asking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 643900.0,
      "end_time": 645196.0,
      "text": "listening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 645220.0,
      "end_time": 648316.0,
      "text": "experimenting, reflecting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 648340.0,
      "end_time": 650820.0,
      "text": "striving and becoming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 652140.0,
      "end_time": 654956.0,
      "text": "What if we each always had something"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 654980.0,
      "end_time": 656500.0,
      "text": "we were working to improve?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 657580.0,
      "end_time": 659996.0,
      "text": "What if we created more low-stakes islands"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 660200.0,
      "end_time": 661220.0,
      "text": "and waters?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 661660.0,
      "end_time": 664116.0,
      "text": "And what if we got clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 664140.0,
      "end_time": 666516.0,
      "text": "within ourselves and with our teammates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 666540.0,
      "end_time": 670750.0,
      "text": "about when we seek to learn and when we seek to perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 670100.0,
      "end_time": 673156.0,
      "text": "so that our efforts can become more consequential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 673180.0,
      "end_time": 675835.0,
      "text": "our improvement never-ending"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 675860.0,
      "end_time": 678140.0,
      "text": "and our best even better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 678820.0,
      "end_time": 680200.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ]
}